form#step2(submit=@step2)
  h1 Almost There!

  p
    Paste in the token you received in your email to publish your space! You'll
    start with a copy of this one. When you arrive at your page you'll need to
    paste in your token again to activate the auto-saving features.

  label
    h3 Your Ticket to Whimsy
    input(value=@token)

  h3
  button(disabled=@progressVisible) Go!

  - if @progressVisible()
    h3
    progress(value=@progress)
